<h1> Youngest director </h1>

<p>
  The youngest director in our dataset right now is 
    <% sorted_director = Director.all.order({ :dob => :desc }) %>
    <% @director_young = sorted_director.first %>
    <a href="/directors/<%= @director_young.id %>"> <%= @director_young.name %> </a>,
    born on <%= @director_young.dob.strftime("%B %w, %Y")%>.
</p>
